verbose_text: For Ru5P, the results obtained by the basic MINLP based R-DFBA are in accordance with the kinetic modeling results and outperform the remaining approaches; on the other hand, the NLP based R-DFBA variants predict a constant amount of Ru5P of about 1 mmol l -1 except for the flux based variant, which also predict a nearly consumed Ru5P after four seconds similar to the kinetic based results.
